        "description": "Explore the cutting-edge of VR with \"Patent Quest,\" developed by TOXI.media in collaboration with PatSnap. This game melds virtual reality with intellectual challenge, perfect for tech enthusiasts and gamers alike.\n\n**Gameplay:**\n\"Patent Quest\" features a novel mechanic where players use their hands or controllers to sort patterns on a VR conveyor belt into the correct categories. Choose from \"Time Trial,\" racing against the clock, or \"Endless,\" where accuracy is critical and a single mistake ends the game.\n\n**Features:**\n- **Intuitive VR Controls:** Natural hand movements or VR controllers provide a deeply immersive experience.\n- **Two Exciting Modes:** Test your skills with Time Trial's pace or Endless mode's precision.\n- **Retro Aesthetics:** Relish in the nostalgic look of Windows 95, combining retro charm with modern VR.\n- **Dynamic Soundtrack:** The original music by Ferm√≠n Delia enhances the immersive experience.\n\n**Why Play?**\n\"Patent Quest\" is a journey into the heart of innovation. Ideal for those who relish technological challenges and retro computing aesthetics.\n\n**Master the art of patent categorization in VR! Available now on the Meta Quest Store.**",
